<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ rbnạ ạjtmạʿnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā rabãnā ạj̊timāʿunā
 biạs̊mika wār̊tibāṭunā
 fī was̊ṭinā ạản̊ta ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 biṣid̊qi waʿ̊dika lanā

[V2]
 2- ạảf̊rāḥanā ʿaẓĩm̊ kadẖā
 taʿ̊zīaẗa ạlrũwḥi lanā
 ạảẓ̊hir̊ bihi rīāsatak̊
 fīnā wāảʿ̊ṭi man̊ tasẖā

[V3]
 3- qud̊nā waqud̊ sujūdanā
 bihi waḥaqĩq̊ lil̊jamīʿ̊
 ḥuḍūraka ạl̊ḥaqã ạlãdẖī
 waʿad̊ta bihi yā samīʿ̊

[V4]
 4- hab̊nā kadẖā taʿaqũlạaⁿ
 waḥik̊maẗaⁿ mina ạl̊ʿulạ
 wal̊yukẖ̊biri ạlrũwḥu bimā
 laka wayuʿ̊ṭinā ʿazā

[V5]
 5- wal̊yuẓ̊hiri ạl̊maj̊da ạlsãnī̃̊
 maj̊da ại̹lahinā ạl̊bahī̃̊
 fī waj̊hika bāhī ạlsãnā
 yā ṣūraẗa ạllhi ạl̊ʿalī̃̊</lyrics>
</song>